Package: clinicalfair
Title: Algorithmic Fairness Assessment for Clinical Prediction Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Cuiwei", "Gao", , "48gaocuiwei@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Evaluates algorithmic fairness of clinical prediction models
    across demographic subgroups. Computes standard fairness metrics
    (demographic parity, equalized odds, calibration parity), generates
    disparity plots, and provides threshold-based mitigation strategies.
    Designed for regulatory compliance with FDA AI/ML guidance and
    health equity assessment. Methods described in Obermeyer et al.
    (2019) <doi:10.1126/science.aax2342> and Rajkomar et al. (2018)
    <doi:10.1056/NEJMms1810169>.
